name: GradationH
description:
GradationH model use GinerMix, UltraColorv4 and Helltaker Lora

GUH3.safetensors (Helltaker Lora * 0.3)

GUH2.safetensors (Helltaker Lora * 0.2)

GUH1.safetensors (Helltaker Lora * 0.1)

GUH0.ckpt (not Mixed Helltaker Lora)

recommendation setting

use [Blue Archive Lora], [Genshin impact Lora]

use [kl-f8-anime VAE]

setting 1, from GinerMix/UltraColorv4

Steps: 30, Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, CFG scale: 10, Size: 512x768 or 768×512, Denoising strength: 0.51, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

setting 2, from Helltaker Lora

Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Size: 512x768, Denoising strength: 0.4, Clip skip: 2

** tip ** 

1. If you use GUH1, recommendation setting1!

2. If you use GUH3, recommendation setting2!

3. If you use GUH2, I respect your choice!

4. When using GUH3, if you use setting1 and blue archive lora
I think the color is not good
